title: Catalonia Sets Independence Vote Deemed Illegal by Spain
description: Sep.26 -- Catalonia is going ahead with plans for a referendum on independence on October 1, despite warnings from Spain's government that the vote is unconstitutional. Bloomberg's Maria Tadeo reports on "Bloomberg Markets: European Close."
